==生平==
塔妮婭·拜倫出生於英國<ref>Bartle, Richard (28 April 2008). We've won: get over it. Retrieved on 29 June 2008 from http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2008/apr/28/games.censorship {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2008/apr/28/games.censorship |date=20210323232024 }}.</ref>，她的父親[[約翰·西奇爾|約翰·西奇爾]]是一位電視電影導演，母親則是一位護士兼模特。<ref>{{cite episode|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03f87bb|title=Professor Tanya Byron|series=[[Desert_Island_Discs|Desert Island Discs]]|network=BBC|station=[[BBC_Radio_4|Radio 4]]|airdate=2013-10-27|accessdate=27 October 2013|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620090655/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03f87bb|dead-url=no}}</ref>

拜倫15歲時祖母被一名吸毒的女人暴虐打擊致死，這成為她開始試圖理解人類行為并進行心理學研究的動機<ref>{{cite episode|title=Saturday Live (includes Tanya Byron as studio guest being interviewed by Fi Glover)|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00sh3fw|series=Saturday Live|serieslink=Saturday Live (radio series)|network=[[BBC|BBC]]|station=[[BBC_Radio_4|Radio 4]]|airdate=2010-05-29|accessdate=29 May 2009|archive-date=2019-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190718123739/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00sh3fw|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來拜倫在[[北倫敦學院學校|北倫敦學院學校]]、[[約克大學|約克大學]]（心理學學士，1989）、[[倫敦大學學院|倫敦大學學院]]（臨床心理學碩士，1992）、[[薩里大學|薩里大學]]（博士，1995）讀書。<ref>UCL alumna to head online child protection review. Retrieved on 29 June 2008 from http://www.ucl.ac.uk/alumni/alumni-news/e_news/enews_september2007 {{Wayback|url=http://www.ucl.ac.uk/alumni/alumni-news/e_news/enews_september2007 |date=20091127161742 }}.</ref><ref name=biog>{{cite web |url=http://www.dcsf.gov.uk/byronreview/biog.shtml |title=Department for Children, Schools and Families : Byron Review |publisher=www.dcsf.gov.uk |accessdate=17 February 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416070632/http://www.dcsf.gov.uk/byronreview/biog.shtml |archivedate=2009年4月16日 }}</ref>

